194
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:22,869
The Intellectual Property Commission says
IP

195
00:09:22,869 --> 00:09:27,709
theft costs the US economy $600 billion dollars
a year,

196
00:09:27,709 --> 00:09:29,550
