dollars a year.

202
00:09:42,070 --> 00:09:43,070
And that’s because

203
00:09:43,070 --> 00:09:46,839
(a) You have to factor in the total future
value.

204
00:09:46,839 --> 00:09:48,389
Not just products sold,

205
00:09:48,389 --> 00:09:51,959
but also the loss of future innovation and
American jobs.

206
00:09:51,959 --> 00:09:52,959
And (b)

207
00:09:52,959 --> 00:09:56,430
A lot of big companies that get hacked, haha,

208
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:59,889
don’t report it publicly because it’s
too embarrassing

209
00:09:59,889 --> 00:10:01,929
and could make stock prices drop.

210
00:10:01,929 --> 00:10:05,579
It’s quite likely that the Chinese military
has hacked

211
00:10:05,579 --> 00:10:08,790
just about every big American corporation.

212
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:11,700
It just doesn’t get publicized.

213
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:13,850
And that’s all for this episode of China
Uncensored.

